      "parameters": {
        "content": "### Pull Side A (HubSpot)\n\nhubspot — `search` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Diff the Two Systems · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 HubSpot private-app token",
