    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### Pull Side B (PostgreSQL)\n\npostgres — `executeQuery` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Diff the Two Systems · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Postgres connection",
